{
  "id": "adv_event_2108_01_02",
  "title": "夏の新曲！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "――うん、いい感じね\nみんな、いったん休憩にしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yep‚ this feels good.\nLet’s all take a short break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.433333333333334,
      "endTime": 11.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ああっ、暑いですわ～\n夏のダンスレッスンは特にキツイですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh* It’s so hot.\nDance lessons in summer are particularly tough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9,
      "endTime": 20.733333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*groan*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.933333333333334,
      "endTime": 23.78333328564962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、エアコンが効いていても\nすぐに汗が噴き出てしまいます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ even with the air conditioning working‚\nI’m running with sweat straight away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.966666666666665,
      "endTime": 29.466666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、ちゃんと水分摂ってね\nスポーツドリンク買ってあるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ don’t forget to stay well hydrated.\nI bought sports drinks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.666666666666668,
      "endTime": 34.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "う～～～～ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*groan*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.233333333333334,
      "endTime": 37.95569160779317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "？　どうかした？　芽衣",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei? Is something wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.166666666666664,
      "endTime": 40.87367340723673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "さっきから、ずーっとうなってますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s been like this for quite a while.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.06666666666667,
      "endTime": 44.36666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "気分でも悪いの？　それとも怪我？\nちゃんと教えて下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you feeling ill? Are you injured?\nTell us already.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.56666666666667,
      "endTime": 51,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "う～～～～～～～～ん……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*groan*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.2,
      "endTime": 55.214988708496094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、私達の声が聞こえてないみたい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like Mei can’t even hear our voices…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4,
      "endTime": 59.30596370697021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、芽衣ちゃん、芽、衣ちゃーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan! Mei-chan‚ Mei-chan Meeeei-chan!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5,
      "endTime": 65.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3966.666666666669
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃあっ！　冷たっ！\nな、何、何？！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eep! It’s cold!\nWh-what was that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 68.16666666666666,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fall-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、なんだ、冷たいペットボトルか\nびっくりしたよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ a chilled plastic bottle on me?\nI’m surprised.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 73.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "やっと、こっちに戻ってきましたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally‚ you’re back with us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.43333333333334,
      "endTime": 75.98333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、どうしたんですか？\nずっと、心ここにあらずって感じでしたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan‚ what’s the matter?\nI’ve had the feeling you weren’t really here for a while now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2,
      "endTime": 81.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "いつもの芽衣らしくないと思うけど……\n芽衣が元気ないと、みんな心配になるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels to me like you’re not your usual self…\nMei‚ we’re all worried that you’re not well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.83333333333333,
      "endTime": 88.2581066608429,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、私達、今、IDOL beach Fes\nに向けて、レッスンしてるじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… Weren’t we doing a lesson to get\nready for IDOL beach Fes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.43333333333334,
      "endTime": 94.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、最高のステージにするために頑張ろうって\n決めたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ we’re working hard to make this the best show we can.\nThat’s what we decided.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.83333333333333,
      "endTime": 100.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "だからこうして自主練を組んで\n今までの曲をおさらいして――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we’re putting together our own practice like this‚\nand polishing up our usual songs.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.23333333333333,
      "endTime": 104.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "今までの曲でいいのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Will our usual songs be good enough?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.53333333333333,
      "endTime": 106.79639454682668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "――え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107,
      "endTime": 108.83333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "だって、福岡のライブは単なるライブじゃないよ！\n夏の祭典だよ！　ビーチ、それにリゾートだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mean‚ the show in Fukuoka isn’t just an ordinary live!\nIt’s a summer music festival! On the beach‚ and in a resort area!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.03333333333333,
      "endTime": 117.41688885158962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "今までの曲の復習も大事だけど、それだけだと\nなんて言うか――サンライズに欠けてない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s important to rehearse our old songs‚ but if that’s all‚\nhow can I put this—won’t it lack sunrise?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.6,
      "endTime": 125.84959351454324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "日の出が欠けるって、どういう意味ですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you mean‚ lack sunrise?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 129.96666657129924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃん、たぶんサプライズを\n言い間違えたんだと思うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan‚ I think she meant\n“surprise”.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.16666666666666,
      "endTime": 135.53333333333336,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "そう！　それそれ！\n私、サプライズが欲しい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! That’s what I meant!\nI want to have a surprise!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.73333333333332,
      "endTime": 139.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "サプライズ……でも、私達は\n歌とダンス以外には、何も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Surprise… but we don’t\ndo anything other than singing and dancing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.6,
      "endTime": 146.20000000000002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "だ・か・ら！　夏らしい新曲を発表するんだよ！\n月のテンペスト、夏の新曲をばばーんと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why! We need to release a summery song!\nLaunch Moon Tempest’s new summer song with a fanfare!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.43333333333334,
      "endTime": 155.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
